ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.
M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: "In the past 7 days, I have been able to laugh and see the funny side of things"
Notes: 0=As much as I always could; 1=Not quite so much now; 2=Definitely not so much now; 3=Not at all; -99=NA; 77=Refused; 88=Missing

ElementDescription: "In the past 7 days, I have looked forward with enjoyment to things"
Notes: 0=As much as I ever did; 1=Rather less than I used to; 2=Definitely less than I used to; 3=Hardly at all; -99=NA; 77=Refused; 88=Missing

ElementDescription: "In the past 7 days, I have blamed myself unnecessarily when things went wrong"
Notes: "0=Yes, most of the time; 1=Yes, some of the time; 2=Not very often; 3=No, never"

ElementDescription: "In the past 7 days, I have been anxious or worried for no good reason"
Notes: "0=No, not at all; 1=Hardly ever; 2=Yes, sometimes; 3=Yes, very often"

ElementDescription: "In the past 7 days, I have felt scared or panicky for no very good reason"
Notes: "0=Yes, quite a lot; 1=Yes, sometimes; 2=No, not much; 3=No, not at all"

ElementDescription: "In the past 7 days, things have been getting on top of me"
Notes: "0=Yes, most of the time I haven't been able to cope at all; 1=Yes, sometimes I haven't been coping as well as usual; 2=No, most of the time I have coped quite well;  3=No, I have been coping as well as ever"

ElementDescription: "In the past 7 days, I have been so unhappy that I have had difficulty sleeping"
Notes: "0=Yes, most of the time; 1=Yes, sometimes; 2=Not very often; 3=No, not at all"

ElementDescription: "In the past 7 days, I have felt sad or miserable"
Notes: "0=Yes, most of the time; 1=Yes, quite often; 2=Not very often; 3=No, not at all"

ElementDescription: "In the past 7 days, I have been so unhappy that I have been crying"
Notes: "0=Yes, most of the time; 1=Yes, quite often; 2=Only occasionally; 3=No, never"

ElementDescription: "In the past 7 days, the thought of harming myself has occurred to me"
